title: Stonesedge
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Western, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Billed as a wholesome comfort food establishment and uses whole food ingredients. Marks the items that are vegetarian and vegan. At lunch there is a vegan burger, a grain bowl, salad; tofu with up-charge. Lunch prices moderate, dinner more expensive.
